<p>We detected
  {{alertType}}
  on your CareerBridge AI account and wanted to notify you immediately.</p>

<div class='alert alert-danger'>
  <strong>Security Alert: {{alertType}}</strong><br />
  {{details}}
</div>

<div class='security-info'>
  <div class='security-info-title'>üîç Event Details</div>
  <div class='security-info-content'>
    <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{timestamp}}</p>
    {{#if ipAddress}}<p><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ipAddress}}</p>{{/if}}
    {{#if location}}<p><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</p>{{/if}}
    {{#if userAgent}}<p><strong>Browser/Device:</strong>
        {{userAgent}}</p>{{/if}}
  </div>
</div>

<div class='alert alert-warning'>
  <strong>Was this you?</strong><br />
  {{#eq alertType 'Successful Login'}}
    If you recognize this activity, no action is needed. If not, please secure
    your account immediately.
  {{else}}
    If you didn't perform this action, your account may be compromised. Please
    take immediate action.
  {{/eq}}
</div>

<div class='content'>
  <strong>Recommended Actions:</strong>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Change your password</strong>
      immediately if you don't recognize this activity</li>
    <li><strong>Enable two-factor authentication</strong>
      for additional security</li>
    <li><strong>Review recent account activity</strong>
      in your security settings</li>
    <li><strong>Log out of all devices</strong>
      if you suspect unauthorized access</li>
    <li><strong>Contact our support team</strong> if you need assistance</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<a href='{{securityUrl}}' class='button'>Review Account Security</a>

<p>If you have any concerns about your account security, please don't hesitate
  to contact our security team immediately.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br />
  <strong>The CareerBridge AI Security Team</strong></p>